<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>认知复杂度 on 编程心语</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/tags/%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6/</link><description>Recent content in 认知复杂度 on 编程心语</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 19 Jul 2026 08:32:30 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ithome.me/tags/%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E5%A4%8D%E6%9D%82%E5%BA%A6/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>代码复杂度度量实战：从圈复杂度到认知复杂度</title><link>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/06/code-complexity-metrics/</link><pubDate>Mon, 06 Jul 2026 08:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ithome.me/post/2026/07/06/code-complexity-metrics/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;我们常说某段代码复杂，但复杂到底怎么衡量？靠感觉？还是靠指标？代码复杂度度量是工程实践中最实用的质量评估手段之一，它能让代码审查从主观判断走向客观数据。本文从两种主流度量方法入手，用实际代码对比分析，帮你建立可落地的复杂度评估体系。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>